ested in normative aspects of state violence.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aPolitical violencexMoral and ethical aspects. 0aState, ThexMoral and ethical aspects. 4aPolitics and Law : Political Philosophy. 4aPolitics and Law : Political Theory. 4aPsychology : Moral Psychology. 4aSociology : Violence. 7aPHILOSOPHY / Political.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978143846677440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438466774423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438466774/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles